{"tid":2125880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張建宗：政府現時無意推居家令或禁足令","createTime":"2020-07-26T13:28:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T13:39:42.000Z","uid":66271,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f7e0c58c2eff1da7b37141e67be43ff132df7d8b","tid":2125880,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T13:28:14.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】政務司司長張建宗重申，現階段政府無意推出居家令或禁足令，又指正竭盡所能在短時間內增加檢疫中心單位數目。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗在網誌表示，如果疫情轉壞，政府會毫不猶豫果斷地採取更嚴厲的管控措施，進一步限制處所營業和減少市民出外的空間，但現階段政府無意推出居家令或禁足令，限制市民外出。<br />\n<br />\n他指會增加檢疫中心單位數目，包括爭取今年年底前在竹篙灣興建多2000個單位，而亞洲國際博覽館亦新增的安老院舍臨時檢疫中心，首個場館可容納100個床位，亦預留了場館可提供額外約350個床位。<br />\n<br />\n他指未來兩星期十分關鍵，呼籲市民盡量留在家中，減少社交接觸和外出用膳，市民切忌心存僥倖，要減少人流聚集，減低病毒在社區傳播的風險。"},{"pid":"87747185d83b8574a7564ff2533157745c8cecf3","tid":2125880,"uid":18999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T13:28:30.000Z","msg":"等回力標"},{"pid":"b9b041a336d34855d5f3861da42c7fd2824a5ae5","tid":2125880,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T13:28:44.000Z","msg":"又中圈套？"},{"pid":"f447b5445db7fc27c4826087cebba37bb938fbb6","tid":2125880,"uid":204227,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T13:29:14.000Z","msg":"因為未到<span class=\"xx-large\">831</span>"},{"pid":"a0f91b62b1dd10490a2bef1941f81344fb791494","tid":2125880,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T13:29:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"395fd59abd10c74f9958126adb802446e06c3907","tid":2125880,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T13:31:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">現時</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"b4bbb7e8982c3bd354bdc59897f10fee0a996117","tid":2125880,"uid":204227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"395fd59abd10c74f9958126adb802446e06c3907","tid":2125880,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T13:31:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">現時</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T13:36:17.000Z","msg":"依加未到8月31<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe49fe9d40d1c4aa1e3d32066432c393d0e643ee","tid":2125880,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T13:39:42.000Z","msg":"借個位唔好意思<br />\n<br />\n可能是全民抗疫的有效方法<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2125449\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2125449</a>"}]}